<BaseLayout
  title="About Barry 'Boomer' Brown - CallBrownsPainting.com"
  description="Learn about Barry 'Boomer' Brown, a 25+ year professional painter serving Brewton, Conecuh, Escambia, and Baldwin Counties in South Alabama. Expert interior and exterior painting services."
  keywords="Barry Boomer Brown painter, about painting contractor Brewton AL, professional painter South Alabama, painting experience"
>
  <main>
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Barry "Boomer" Brown</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Professional painter with 25+ years of experience serving South Alabama communities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
      <div class="container">
        <article>
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>
            CallBrownsPainting.com was founded by Barry "Boomer" Brown, a professional painter with over 25 years of experience 
            in the South Alabama region. Based in Brewton, Alabama, Boomer has built a reputation for quality workmanship and 
            reliable service throughout Conecuh, Escambia, and Baldwin Counties.
          </p>
          <p>
            What started as a local painting business has grown to serve communities across South Alabama, including Evergreen, 
            Flomaton, Atmore, Monroeville, Bay Minette, Loxley, Stapleton, Robertsdale, Summerdale, Foley, Silver Hill, Fairhope, 
            Daphne, Spanish Fort, Gulf Shores, and Orange Beach.
          </p>

          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            To provide exceptional interior and exterior painting services that enhance the beauty and value of homes, businesses, 
            churches, schools, and gymnasiums throughout South Alabama. We are committed to using premium materials, proven techniques, 
            and professional craftsmanship on every project.
          </p>

          <h2>Why Choose CallBrownsPainting.com</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>25+ Years Experience:</strong> Decades of professional painting expertise in South Alabama</li>
            <li><strong>Local Knowledge:</strong> Understanding of Alabama's coastal climate and painting challenges</li>
            <li><strong>Quality Materials:</strong> Premium paints and supplies for lasting results</li>
            <li><strong>Reliable Service:</strong> On-time completion and professional communication</li>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive Coverage:</strong> Interior and exterior painting for all property types</li>
            <li><strong>Free Estimates:</strong> No-obligation quotes for all projects</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-hero {
      padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .about-content {
      padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
    }

    .about-content article {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
